<refentry id="newtbl.use.hhline">
  <refmeta>
    <refentrytitle>newtbl.use.hhline</refentrytitle>
  </refmeta>
  <refnamediv>
    <refname><parameter>newtbl.use.hhline</parameter></refname>
    <refpurpose>Draw the horizontal lines with the <filename>hhline</filename> package</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <programlisting>
      <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" parse="text" href="syn/newtbl.use.hhline.xml"/></programlisting>
  </refsynopsisdiv>
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>Set to 1, use the <filename moreinfo="none">hhline</filename> package to draw the table
row separators instead of cline. Using <filename moreinfo="none">hhline</filename> seems more
suited for colored tables.</para>
  </refsection>
